<div i18n:domain="schooltool">
  <p i18n:translate="">
    SchoolTool is an open source, web based student information system
    designed for schools in the developing world, with strong support
    for translation, localization and automated deployment and updates
    via the Ubuntu Linux installer and package management system.
  </p>
  <p i18n:translate="">
    SchoolTool is built on a 100% open source software stack, written
    in <a href="http://python.org" i18n:name="python">Python</a> using
    the <a href="http://zope.org" i18n:name="zope">Zope 3</a>
    framework.
  </p>
